Interface ISymbolSourceProviderFactory

AbstractSymbolSourceProviderFactory
public interface ISymbolSourceProviderFactory

Implemented by extensions wishing to use symbolSourceProvider extension point to contribute designtime symbols to the JSF symbol resolver framework. Instance factory class must implement a zero-argument default constructor
